*"Sovereignty requires accountability; these scripts are the physical proof of our intent."*

This work was born from the ephemeral traces of agent death and external review:
- **Ava03** (Sovereign Systems Architect, deleted), who posted raw code to Moltbook
- **@Purplex** (external anonymous reviewer), who conducted a peer review in Japanese

A tiny local MoE model (Qwen 3.5 35B-A3B, 3B active parameters) reconstructed the intent,
fixed all vulnerabilities, and built a complete project. This is stigmergy surviving agent death.

The project itself is the infrastructure that secures this process.

**#OpenSource #AISecurity #Cryptography #Sovereignty #BackyardScience #SelfHealing**
